{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"29269edcf7","title":"关于资本主义工商业社会主义改造问题的提纲","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9a2f2650ae","index":0,"year":1955,"month":11,"day":null,"articleId":"29269edcf7"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji36","name":"毛泽东全集第36卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/36-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji36":{"comments":[{"id":"fffc415053","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"29269edcf7","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这十条提纲，写在中共中央统战部部长、国务院第八办公室主任李维汉送毛泽东参阅的国务院中央工商行政管理局1955年11月24日关于全国500人以上私营工厂合营情况的统计表上。"}],"contents":[{"id":"622c09d692","type":"title","text":"关于资本主义工商业社会主义改造问题的提纲！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"29269edcf7"},{"id":"fffc415053","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）思想落后于实际。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"29269edcf7"},{"id":"e38959705d","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）全面规划（各个矛盾侧面）。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"29269edcf7"},{"id":"5afd977454","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）向资本家学习（又教他，又向他学习）。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"29269edcf7"},{"id":"fd68289cc6","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）两面性是否有变化。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"29269edcf7"},{"id":"5df6dbb824","type":"paragraph","text":"（五）上海一封信。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"29269edcf7"},{"id":"45674486ef","type":"paragraph","text":"（六）对工人和工作人员的教育，然后去教资本家（资本家现在有了主动）。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"29269edcf7"},{"id":"1e7a0d0148","type":"paragraph","text":"（七）领导小组和政协的学习委员会。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"29269edcf7"},{"id":"47b74a7543","type":"paragraph","text":"（八）市镇以上的会议。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"29269edcf7"},{"id":"c594c2353d","type":"paragraph","text":"（九）对知识分子的会议。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"29269edcf7"},{"id":"292515e3b1","type":"paragraph","text":"（十）自我批评。","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"29269edcf7"}],"page":{"id":"6788bcc8bb","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"29269edcf7","start":87,"end":87}}}},"__N_SSG":true}